'''Galacticon Insurance''' was a company that sold [[Insurer|insurance]].

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Galacticon Insurance was removed when [[Riders of the Maelstrom (adventure)|''Riders of the Maelstrom'']] was reprinted in ''[[Classic Adventures: Volume Three]]''. The reference was replaced with a mention of generic insurance payments, rather than identifying a specific company.

